body:
Emergency Commissions

Hi! This is Han and I’m opening emergency commissions because my d/d left and we need some pocket money for little groceries and stuff bc we are going to be stunted considering he was a big source of the money we had to live off of

My prices are $6 a full piece! fully colored; bust or full body is up to you!

I don’t do anything NSFW or just hateful and disturbing, or any mechs

I do real people, original characters, self insert, fan art, furries, etc.

No extra charge for characters but I’ll only do up to 3!

Buy Badweatherfriend a Coffee. ko-fi.com/badweatherfriend

summary: It’s been a while since I last tried doing a traditional piece, even if it was just a sketch. So, I decided my first two dragons...
body:
It’s been a while since I last tried doing a traditional piece, even if it was just a sketch. So, I decided my first two dragons in Flight Rising. I only starting last month, but so far I’m enjoying these wonderful dragons. Plus, it gave me an excuse to draw my favorite mythical creature again.

Hummingbird is the one I customized, while Lavrenti is her randomly generated mate. Might try drawing again digitally to make it better.
